OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe low
OL,6,Fcloud around the east coast moving
OL,7,Finland in places. Staying dry with the
OL,8,Fclear skies through the Trossachs and
OL,9,Fwest, winds remaining light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FAny low cloud should clear
OL,12,Fduring the morning with bright and
OL,13,Fsunny spells developing. Temperatures
OL,14,Fdown a bit, but still warm or very
OL,15,Fwarm in any sunshine. Light northwest
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
